"Y-m-d\"",[104,1601,1602],{"class":128},") ",[104,1604,1342],{"class":110},[104,1606,1607],{"class":124}," \".\u003C\u002Fp>\"",[104,1609,129],{"class":128},[104,1611,1612],{"class":106,"line":338},[104,1613,423],{"class":110},[104,1615,1616,1618,1620],{"class":106,"line":358},[104,1617,271],{"class":110},[104,1619,292],{"class":114},[104,1621,173],{"class":110},[104,1623,1624,1626,1628],{"class":106,"line":367},[104,1625,271],{"class":110},[104,1627,181],{"class":114},[104,1629,173],{"class":110},[17,1631,1632,1633,1636,1637,1640],{},"This embeds PHP in HTML to output the current date — letting us dynamically display content. Note: PHP files have ",[101,1634,1635],{},".php"," extension, not ",[101,1638,1639],{},".html",". PHP code needs server-side compilation before the result (HTML) is sent to the browser.",[17,1642,1643,1644,1646],{},"That's also why early web pages had a brief \"blank flash\" between pages — when you submit a request, PHP needs to execute the ",[101,1645,1635],{}," file, convert results to HTML, then send to browser. Slight delay.",[17,1648,1649],{},"This is also why AJAX emerged later — letting us dynamically update content without reloading the whole page.",[17,1651,1652],{},"Why was PHP so popular?",[1654,1655,1656,1663,1669,1675],"ol",{},[1657,1658,1659,1662],"li",{},[52,1660,1661],{},"Easy to learn:"," simple syntax, beginner-friendly.",[1657,1664,1665,1668],{},[52,1666,1667],{},"Open source and free:"," no expensive license fees, attractive to companies.",[1657,1670,1671,1674],{},[52,1672,1673],{},"Strong community support:"," PHP has a huge community (very active as far as I know).",[1657,1676,1677,1680],{},[52,1678,1679],{},"Designed for web development:"," built-in features for web — DB connections, form handling, etc.",[17,1682,1683],{},"Every language has pros and cons. PHP is no exception — but I'd say...",[17,1685,1686],{},"\"It's not that PHP itself is bad — it's that PHP is too easy to misuse.\"",[17,1688,1689],{},"That's my summary of PHP.",[36,1691,1693],{"id":1692},"closing-thoughts","Closing thoughts",[17,1695,1696],{},"I recently revisited my capstone code from years ago — total dark history. Code was chaos, no structure, full of SQL Injection vulnerabilities. Genuinely painful to look at~~~",[36,1698,1700],{"id":1699},"also-published","Also published",[17,1702,1703],{},"This article is also published on:",[1705,1706,1707,1714,1721,1728,1735,1742],"ul",{},[1657,1708,1709],{},[21,1710,1713],{"href":1711,"rel":1712},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Ftags\u002FCode-Review-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%92%E6%98%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%9E%E3%80%8E%E5%97%B6%E3%80%8F%E8%81%B2%E9%96%8B%E5%95%9F%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E8%BB%9F%E9%AB%94%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF\u002F",[25],"Is Ray Not Array (in Mandarin)",[1657,1715,1716],{},[21,1717,1720],{"href":1718,"rel":1719},"https:\u002F\u002Fithelp.ithome.com.tw\u002Fusers\u002F20119486\u002Fironman\u002F8232",[25],"Code Review of My Youth on IT Home (in Mandarin)",[1657,1722,1723],{},[21,1724,1727],{"href":1725,"rel":1726},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.threads.com\u002F@isray_notarray",[25],"Threads — Soft skills posts",[1657,1729,1730],{},[21,1731,1734],{"href":1732,"rel":1733},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.facebook.com\u002Fisraynotarray",[25],"Facebook — Meme posts",[1657,1736,1737],{},[21,1738,1741],{"href":1739,"rel":1740},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.instagram.com\u002Fisraynotarray\u002F",[25],"Instagram — Memes + soft skills",[1657,1743,1744],{},[21,1745,1748],{"href":1746,"rel":1747},"https:\u002F\u002Fportaly.cc\u002Fisraynotarray",[25],"Portaly — Landing page",[1750,1751,1752],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sOudu, html code.shiki .sOudu{--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-default:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .stw71, html code.shiki .stw71{--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-default:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sWayO, html code.shiki .sWayO{--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-default:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki